    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras/3829058f5b47cb5ecc0de52ab0fdb616.avif?t=1731637568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras_big/3829058f5b47cb5ecc0de52ab0fdb616.avif?t=1731637568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A casual card game</strong> where you use note cards and various items to combine cards and create Whole Note Cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras/9f8c6ae188a15f9f59d33f5ea1b31bbe.avif?t=1731637568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras_big/9f8c6ae188a15f9f59d33f5ea1b31bbe.avif?t=1731637568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Note Cards and Item Cards to create a <strong>Whole Note Card</strong>, earn coins, and reach the highest score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Focus on the two cards you can combine!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras/bca70a347d5f458814eba3705f48a2ac.avif?t=1731637568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259710/extras_big/bca70a347d5f458814eba3705f48a2ac.avif?t=1731637568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the game in <strong>two modes</strong>: Studio and Artisan !</p>",
